# 🌐 Data Source

All protein datasets and annotations were retrieved from the official UniProt Knowledgebase (UniProtKB), one of the world’s leading protein information resources.

## Official Databases
- UniProt: https://www.uniprot.org
- RCSB Protein Data Bank: https://www.rcsb.org

